=\"lazy\" class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_image\" src=\"/assets/76.png\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"team-header_background-icon-wrapper-copy\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.25\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" class=\"team-header_background-icon-copy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/6924418b395e9ab3d12cfac8_shape-2.svg\"></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>Committed to delivering the best outcome for you</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Michelle Eyre is a Chartered Legal Executive in our Real Estate Litigation team. She joined us in 2023, bringing over two decades of experience in the property industry.</p><p>‍</p><p>Michelle qualified in 2015 after spending 17 years at a major international law firm working across its Sheffield and Kampala offices. She later moved to a specialist property litigation practice before joining us. Her background gives her a deep understanding of the commercial property sector and a practical, down-to-earth approach to resolving disputes.</p><p>‍</p><p>She advises a wide range of clients including landowners, occupiers, financial institutions and retailers and regularly helps clients navigate issues around rights of way, breaches of covenant and forfeiture, always aiming to resolve disputes efficiently and with minimal disruption.</p><p>‍</p><p>Her experience spans all areas of real estate litigation, from lease renewals and break rights to adverse possession, trespass and nuisance claims</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section class=\"section_expertise-video w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen is-light\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"expertise-video_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid expertise-video_content\"><div class=\"expertise-video_content-left\"><h2 class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></h2><p class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></p></div><div class=\"expertise-video_content-right\"><div class=\"expertise-image_wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/plugins/Basic/assets/placeholder.60f9b1840c.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image w-dyn-bind-empty\"></div><a href=\"/michelle-eyre#\" class=\"expertise-video_lightbox w-inline-block w-dyn-bind-empty w-lightbox\"><img src=\"michelle-eyre.html\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"expertise-video_lightbox-image w-dyn-bind-empty\"><div class=\"lightbox-play-icon\"><div class=\"icon-embed-large w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5.33301 32C5.33301 17.2724 17.2721 5.33334 31.9997 5.33334C39.0721 5.33334 45.8549 8.14286 50.8559 13.1438C55.8568 18.1448 58.6663 24.9276 58.6663 32C58.6663 46.7276 46.7273 58.6667 31.9997 58.6667C17.2721 58.6667 5.33301 46.7276 5.33301 32ZM27.1198 43.4134L42.6664 33.7067C43.2482 33.3341 43.6001 32.6909 43.6001 32C43.6001 31.3092 43.2482 30.6659 42.6664 30.2934L27.0664 20.5867C26.452 20.1993 25.6758 20.1755 25.0388 20.5244C24.4018 20.8734 24.004 21.5403 23.9998 22.2667V41.7334C23.9912 42.4774 24.3963 43.1647 25.0514 43.5174C25.7065 43.8702 26.5033 43.8301 27.1198 43.4134Z\" fill=\"CurrentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div><div class=\"lightbox_overlay\"></div><script type=\"application/json\" class=\"w-json\">{\n  \"items\": [],\n  \"group\": \"\"\n}</script></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\